This extension needs a modification for Acumatica 2021R1.  The following changes will make it compatible with 2021R1.

BusinessAccountMaintPXKBExt : 
   Replace the following lines:
         21       if (Base.converToCustomer.GetEnabled())
         22           Base.converToCustomer.PressButton(adapter);
   with:
         21       if (Base.Actions["ExtendToCustomer"].GetEnabled())
         22           Base.Actions["ExtendToCustomer"].Press();

   Replace the following lines:
         48       if (Base.converToVendor.GetEnabled())
         49           Base.converToVendor.PressButton(adapter);
   with:      
         48       if (Base.Actions["ExtendToVendor"].GetEnabled())
         49           Base.Actions["ExtendToVendor"].Press();

CustomerMaintPXKBExt :
   Replace the following lines:
         20       if (Base.extendToVendor.GetEnabled())
         21           Base.extendToVendor.Press();
   with:
         20       if (Base.Actions["ExtendToVendor"].GetEnabled())
         21           Base.Actions["ExtendToVendor"].Press();

VendorMaintPXKBExt :
   Replace the following lines:
         20       if (Base.extendToCustomer.GetEnabled())
         21           Base.extendToCustomer.Press();
   with:
         20       if (Base.Actions["ExtendToCustomer"].GetEnabled())
         21           Base.Actions["ExtendToCustomer"].Press();
